### Dashboard API Tests
@url = http://127.0.0.1:3000

### ============= CORE DASHBOARD ENDPOINTS =============

### Get Monthly Assessments (Default: 4 months with competency breakdown)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments

### Get Monthly Assessments (Last 6 months)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments?months=6

### Get Monthly Assessments (Last 12 months)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments?months=12

### Get Monthly Assessments (Filter by Provinsi)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments?months=6&provinsi_id=31

### Get Monthly Assessments (Filter by Sektor)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments?months=6&sektor=Digital Marketing

### Get Monthly Assessments (Filter by TUK)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments?months=6&id_tuk=348

### Get Monthly Assessments (All Filters)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments?months=12&provinsi_id=31&sektor=Digital Marketing&id_tuk=348

### Get Sertifikat Per Skema (Default: Top 10)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/sertifikat-per-skema

### Get Sertifikat Per Skema (Top 5)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/sertifikat-per-skema?limit=5

### Get Sertifikat Per Skema (Filter tahun 2025)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/sertifikat-per-skema?tahun=2025

### Get Sertifikat Per Skema (Filter tahun 2026)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/sertifikat-per-skema?tahun=2026

### Get Sertifikat Per Skema (Sort ascending)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/sertifikat-per-skema?sort=asc&limit=10

### Get Sertifikat Per Skema (Kombinasi: Top 15, tahun 2025, desc)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/sertifikat-per-skema?limit=15&tahun=2025&sort=desc

### Get Sertifikat Per Skema (All bidang - limit 50)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/sertifikat-per-skema?limit=50

### Get Penyebaran TUK (Default: Top 20)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/penyebaran-tuk

### Get Penyebaran TUK (Top 10)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/penyebaran-tuk?limit=100

### Get Penyebaran TUK (Filter by jenis_tuk)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/penyebaran-tuk?jenis_tuk=Mandiri

### Get Penyebaran TUK (Sort ascending)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/penyebaran-tuk?sort=asc&limit=15

### Get Penyebaran TUK (All filters)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/penyebaran-tuk?limit=30&jenis_tuk=TUK Sewaktu&sort=desc

### Get Penyebaran Mitra (Default: Top 20)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/penyebaran-mitra

### Get Penyebaran Mitra (Top 10)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/penyebaran-mitra?limit=10

### Get Penyebaran Mitra (Sort ascending)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/penyebaran-mitra?sort=asc&limit=15

### Get Penyebaran Mitra (Top 50)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/penyebaran-mitra?limit=50

### Get Asesor Distribution (Default: All provinces, only approved assessors)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/asesor-distribution

### Get Asesor Distribution (Top 10 Provinces)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/asesor-distribution?limit=10

### Get Asesor Distribution (Sort ascending)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/asesor-distribution?sort=asc&limit=15

### Get Asesor Distribution (Include invalid assessors)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/asesor-distribution?include_invalid=true

### Get Asesor Distribution (Top 5, with invalid assessors)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/asesor-distribution?limit=5&include_invalid=true&sort=desc

### ============= ADDITIONAL DASHBOARD API TESTS =============

### Get Dashboard Summary (Current Month)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/summary

### Get Dashboard Summary (Current Month - Explicit)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/summary?period=current_month

### Get Dashboard Summary (Current Year)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/summary?period=current_year

### Get Statistik Overview
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/statistik-overview

### Get Distribusi Sektor (Default: Top 5)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/distribusi-sektor

### Get Distribusi Sektor (Top 10)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/distribusi-sektor?limit=10

### Get Asesor Stats
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/asesor-stats

### Get LSP Count
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/lsp-count

### Get Monthly Assessments with Competency (Default: 4 months)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments

### Get Monthly Assessments with Competency (Last 6 months)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments?months=6

### Get Monthly Assessments with Competency (Filter by Provinsi)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments?months=12&provinsi_id=31

### Get Monthly Assessments with Competency (Filter by Sektor)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments?months=6&sektor=Teknologi Informasi

### Get Monthly Assessments with Competency (All Filters)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/monthly-assessments?months=12&provinsi_id=31&sektor=TIK&id_lsp=1565&id_tuk=348

### Get Penyebaran Regional (By Island)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/penyebaran-regional

### Get Trends Comparison (Default: All metrics, Previous Month)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/trends

### Get Trends Comparison (Previous Month)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/trends?metric=all&compare_period=previous_month

### Get Trends Comparison (Previous Year)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/trends?metric=all&compare_period=previous_year

### Get Trends Comparison (Specific Metric)
GET {{url}}/api/dashboard/trends?metric=asesmen&compare_period=previous_month
